    Page: 186
    Verse: 3
Tags:
  - God
---
Life is not an end in itself. Your goal is not conformed to this material
world in which your body is living. Your goal goes beyond this world of
appearances. Your goal is the attainment of Divine Perfection, which is the
nature of absolute peace and joy.
